{"tid":2047243,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"想問下97之後有幾多黑警謀殺香港市民係要坐監？","createTime":"2020-06-02T03:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T02:09:38.000Z","uid":198278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c1dcf2aafe97d91475a8c64fc4f008561d5cff","tid":2047243,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"啲藍屍五毛都on99<br />\n成日拎美國同香港嚟比較<br />\n盲係度話美國警暴如何如何<br />\n話民主冇用之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日扮盲又唔知<br />\n美國警察故意殺人係要受法律制裁<br />\n香港呢？<br />\n的士司機同南亞人畀黑警粗暴對待致死<br />\n法治呢？<br />\nSorry 呢度係香港 唔係美國<br />\n佢地殺人最多去到死因裁判處<br />\n然後&hellip; Who cares??<br />\n更加唔使講個啲被自殺嘅無辜市民<br />\n一句「死因冇可疑」就不了了之&hellip;"},{"pid":"1a70beca9023c420d98ffe9e899fb4433efadecf","tid":2047243,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"宜家直頭係唔會被起訴<br />\n家族式藏毒販毒律政司一句撒控理由都唔使比<br />\n<br />\n揸電單車撞人仲可以升職加薪"},{"pid":"f022c63e8049e3a517547e447040436281532f44","tid":2047243,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"係林鄭月娥隻臭雞先咁不知廉恥<br />\n令香港崩潰嘅法治 去同美國比較<br />\n近得中共多 禮樂崩壞到冇感覺"},{"pid":"31fc27c7bd79486e6a41b494658c0623847c2352","tid":2047243,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"學埋中共啲「依法治國」<br />\n執法者唔需要守法        <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都on99"},{"pid":"ed548c65b9c4ac26ad6aba0adfa98f5ba8540c8c","tid":2047243,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b08bc50ebe4aca0f29658b8d03e044b0b28fc96","tid":2047243,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c3c305f54b09681045c285bd999ec690206f3f","tid":2047243,"uid":198278,"lik